title: 273: Combine Preview: Defense
itunes:title: 273: Combine Preview: Defense
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks kick off the podcast by scrutinizing Sam Darnold's decision not to throw at the 2018 NFL Scouting Combine (4:09). The guys then take a look at the defensive prospects set to take Indianapolis by storm (9:44). Who will create the most buzz? Who is flying under the radar? All that and much more on this episode of Move the Sticks.
